Phase 2: Student Learning Interface (4 pages)
Focus: Students can access classes and content
My Classes Section (/dashboard/classes)
Fetch today's classes from daily_classes table
3 cards: Maths, Physics, Chemistry with teacher info
"Attend Class" buttons → YouTube live links
Recorded Classes Section (/dashboard/recordings)
Date picker filter
Fetch from recorded_classes table
Display 3 subject cards with "Watch Recording" buttons
Doubts Classes Section (/dashboard/doubts)
Conditional access - only if has_doubts_access = true
Fetch upcoming sessions from doubts_classes table
"Join Doubts Class" → Google Meet links
Profile Section (/dashboard/profile)
Display student details from users table
Show batch info, statistics (tests attempted, avg score)

Phase 3: Testing System (3 pages)
Focus: Students can take and review exams
Tests Section (/dashboard/tests)
List all exams from exams table
Show student's scores from exam_attempts
Buttons: Attempt / Retake / View Result
Test Attempt Page (/dashboard/test/:exam_id/attempt)
Timer, question navigation (1-160)
Fetch questions from questions table
Auto-save to student_responses table
Submit → Calculate score → Insert into exam_attempts
View Result Page (/dashboard/test/:exam_id/result)
Show score and detailed answers
Fetch from student_responses + questions (JOIN)
Highlight correct/wrong/unanswered

